reviewText: I am a big Bleach fan so all of there shows are the best. I would recommend this anime to anyone wanting a good show to watch.
Sadly the aspect ratio is still 1.33:1 ...the anime changed to 16:9 during the Amagai Shusuke arc. (ep 168). Though it remains a great example of anime.
It was a good filler arc with lots of action. I can't wait for the 18th Box set! I would recommend this to any Bleach fan. 255 episodes and counting!!!

The box art just screams Rangiku shouting out "Growl Haineko" to me. I absolutely loved the Zanpakut rebellion arc although I think they did sorta drag it on too long and place it in the wrong time to show but still great.

If you want the full Bleach experience, then add this to your collection. No, it is not the main story arc, but still great episodes. I rarely find an episode I don't like. I, like everyone else, wish they did entire arcs, seasons, whatever in each set release, but lets face it, we would do the same if it was our cash cow. So, don't hate too much. You can always watch the subs on Hulu or Internet.
